The Wind That Shakes the Barley;;87;;90;;NC;;In 1920s Ireland young doctor Damien O'Donovan (Cillian Murphy) prepares to depart for a new job in a London hospital. As he says his goodbyes at a friend's farm, British Black and Tans arrive, and a young man is killed. Damien joins his brother Teddy (Padraic Delaney) in the Irish Republican Army, but political events are soon set in motion that tear the brothers apart.;;History,Drama;;Ken Loach;;2006;;Cillian Murphy,Padraic Delaney,Liam Cunningham,Orla Fitzgerald,Mary Riordan,Mary Murphy,Laurence Barry,Damien Kearney,Máirtín de Cógáin,Myles Horgan,Martin Lucey,William Ruane,Roger Allam,Frank Bourke;;https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/wind_that_shakes_the_barley